    • getColumnsSize

      public int getColumnsSize()
      Returns the number of columns for this GridPane mask. The number of columns for a GridPane is the max of : - the number of column constraints - the max column index defined in this GridPane children + 1
      Returns:
      the number of columns

    • getRowsSize
